It can be used as a standalone or in a CI process.
It's configurable and of course as an open source project, you can customise and participate by pushing Pull Requests.
As one of the maintainers of this tool suite, I will provide an overview of the link checking process as well as a tour of the reasons why you should care about your links and a demo of how this specific tool works.&lt;/p&gt;</abstract>
