        <track>MySQL</track>
        <type>devroom</type>
        <language/>
        <abstract>&lt;p&gt;This session reveals four experimental Vitess developments that automate away complex database operations. With these developments Vitess is able to run its own database infrastructure, transparently to the user, and take control of risky and elaborate situations and operations.&lt;/p&gt;

