        <abstract>&lt;p&gt;Have you always wanted a flexible &amp;amp; interactive visualization that is easy for others to work with without handling all the Javascript libraries? Or do you want to build a user interface for your Machine Learning Model? This talk has you covered with building data apps in Python using Streamlit with examples of a Travel Visualization App using Google Maps Data &amp;amp; an UI for the ImageNet Model.&lt;/p&gt;</abstract>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;In this talk, I showcase couple of different use cases where you can build your data focussed applications using Streamlit, an open source library in pure Python.&lt;/p&gt;

