&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.wireguard.com/"&gt;WireGuard&lt;/a&gt; is a new VPN technology created by Jason A. Donenfeld that is getting popular thanks to its simplicity.&lt;/p&gt;</abstract>
