        <slug>ow2_ggi_2</slug>
        <title>OW2 OSS Good Governance initiative</title>
        <subtitle/>
        <track>OW2 Open Source Community stand</track>
        <type>standtrack</type>
        <language/>
        <abstract>&lt;p&gt;Presentation of OW2 GGI: Good Governance Initiative&lt;/p&gt;</abstract>
        <description>&lt;p&gt;The OW2 Open Source Good Governance Initiative (GGI) is a joint effort between OW2 members and non-members to grow awareness and expertise on how to properly use and contribute to open source software with the objective to improve competitiveness and enhance the sustainability of the European OSS ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Get started here:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OSS Good Governance resource center: &lt;a href="https://www.ow2.org/view/OSS_Governance/"&gt;https://www.ow2.org/view/OSS_Governance/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OW2 Open Source Good Governance Initiative slide deck: &lt;a href="https://www.ow2.org/download/Events/FOSDEM_2021/2102-FOSDEM-OW2-GGI-Intro.pdf"&gt;https://www.ow2.org/download/Events/FOSDEM_2021/2102-FOSDEM-OW2-GGI-Intro.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;OW2 Open Source Good Governance initiative video primer (5:34): &lt;a href="https://youtu.be/abQzK8gkZJU"&gt;https://youtu.be/abQzK8gkZJU&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
